title: Pokémon Presents | 8.18.21
author: The Official Pokémon YouTube channel
description:
The latest news about Pokémon games and apps! 

Featuring announcements for: Pokémon Brilliant Diamond and Pokémon Shining Pearl, Pokémon Legends: Arceus, Pokémon GO, Pokémon Masters EX, Pokémon Café ReMix, and Pokémon HOME.

Originally premiered on August 18, 2021 at 6:00 a.m. PDT.
